name: Frogs vs. Storks
summary: In Frogs vs. Storks you play with your little frogs that make a good and peaceful living in their beautiful pond. But, with the arrival of storks, the pond became a dangerous place to live! Storks are everywhere now just waiting for their chance to eat your frogs! Outsmart evil storks and once again make you pond a peaceful place to live in Frogs vs. Storks.
